Text: RE Glad to see youPST I actually have the time to have a life I never knew there was such a thing Ive been reading about all the events going on down there and have been thinking about all my friends that are effected Just came back from Canada last week Went on a skiing trip to Whistler outside of Vancouver I t is one of the best resorts in North America Tommorow Im going to LA for a convention and then Im off to Europe to see my sister and her new baby whenever it decides to be born So all in all things are great From To Subject RE Glad to see you Date Mon Jan We lost about to layoffs and we lost about to the estate staying with Enron The remaining people are going to UBS We will see what happens How are things with you Talk to you later PL Original Message From Rahmaan Mwongozi ENRON Sent Thursday January PM To Love Phillip M Subject Glad to see you Glad to see that you are still working Was the fallout big on the floor Whos still around Send and receive Hotmail on your mobile device Click Here File bqlhmtagetlENasp This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at
